    {
      "id": "freeText_1773167504282",
      "text": "## Schema\n\n### Loopbacks\n- **Loopback0**\n  - Fabric A: **10.254.1.<NodeID>/32**\n  - Fabric B: **10.254.2.<NodeID>/32**\n- **Loopback1**\n  - Fabric A: **10.255.1.<NodeID>/32**\n  - Fabric B: **10.255.2.<NodeID>/32**\n\n### MLAG\n- Domain ID: **100**\n- Peer-Link: **Port-Channel1000**\n- Peer Sync Interface: **Vlan4094**\n- Peer Sync Prefix: **169.254.0.0/30**\n- Peer OSPF Peering Interface: **Vlan4093**\n- Peer OSPF Peering Prefix: **192.0.0.0/30**\n\n### First-Hop IRB\n- FHRP Model: **vARP**\n- VIP: **10.<VLAN-ID>.<VLAN-ID>.1**\n- vMAC: **001c.7300.0001**\n\n### Spanning-Tree\n- Mode: **MST**\n\n### Inter-Fabric IP Transport\n  - Point-to-Point IP Block: **172.16.255.0/24**\n  - Routing Protocol: **OSPF (Area 0)**\n\n",
      "position": {
        "x": -445.4290308338521,
        "y": -345.8160614413282
      },
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontColor": "#000000",
      "backgroundColor": "#f5f5f5",
      "fontWeight": "normal",
      "fontStyle": "normal",
      "textDecoration": "none",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "fontFamily": "Arial"
    },
    {
      "id": "freeText_1773191456774",
      "text": "## Node IDs\n\n**Fabric A:**\n- A-SPINE1: **1**\n- A-SPINE2: **2**\n\n**Fabric B:**\n- B-SPINE1: **1**\n- B-SPINE2: **2**",
